.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: corn, broccoli, blueberry, zucchini, plum
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, puzzles, fishing, card-games
5 different games are played: cornmaster, go, whist, monopoly, billiard
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, volleyball, snowboarding, rugby, basketball
1. the british is the person eating blueberry
2. the swedish is the person who's sport is snowboarding
3. the danish is the person who's hobby is fishing
4. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating zucchini
5. the person eating broccoli is the person who's hobby is woodworking
6. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is volleyball
7. the person eating plum is the person playing go
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball
11. the person who's sport is basketballs is on the left or right of the person playing go
12. the person playing cornmaster is the person who's hobby is dancing
13. the german is the person playing monopoly
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person eating corn
15. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    plum	|     corn	|      blueberry	|     broccoli	|     zucchini	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Sport		|     handball	|    basketball	|     volleyball	|     rugby	|      snowboarding	|
| Hobby	|    card-games	|     fishing	|     puzzles	|    woodworking	|      dancing	|
| Game		|   go	|    billiard	|  whist	|    monopoly	|   cornmaster	|
